dct_title_s: Denny's pocket map of San Mateo County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Pocket map of San Mateo County, California
Map of San Mateo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Edward Denny & Co., map publishers.
Shows ranchos, township and section lines, tracts, roads, railroads, trails, lighthouses, schools, parks, rivers and creeks.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
